tiles.title: Estimate vCore Used (30s Window) - Last 3 days

queries.text:
_applicationSummary
| project Timestamp,AppId
| make-series Runs=dcount(AppId) on Timestamp step 1h

_applicationSummary
| extend AppName_ = extract(@"^([^_]+)_", 1, AppName)
| summarize dcount(AppName) by AppName_

let _capacity = _maxCapacityCU * 2 * 3;
let _timespan = timespan(30s);
let vCore = materialize (
RawLogs
| where todatetime(records["timestamp"]) > ago(5d)
| where tostring(records["category"]) == "EventLog"
| where isnotempty(records.["properties"].["Executor Info"].["Total Cores"])
| where tostring(records.["properties"].["Event"]) == "SparkListenerExecutorAdded"
| extend vCores = toint(records.["properties"].["Executor Info"].["Total Cores"])
| summarize VcorePerExec=max(vCores) by applicationId=tostring(records["applicationId"])
);
let app_time = RawLogs
| where  isnotempty(tostring(records["applicationId"]))
| distinct applicationId=tostring(records["applicationId"]), timestamp=todatetime(records["timestamp"]), executorId=tostring(records.["executorId"]) , capacityId=tostring(records.["capacityId"]);
app_time
| where applicationId in (vCore | project applicationId)
| summarize  Executors=count_distinct(executorId)  by  bin(timestamp,_timespan), applicationId, capacityId
| lookup vCore on applicationId
| extend vCore = VcorePerExec*Executors
| make-series vCores = sum(vCore), Max=_capacity default = "" on timestamp step _timespan by capacityId
| extend ['Max vCore'] = series_fill_forward(Max)

SparkDriverLogs
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| extend AppName_ = extract(@"^([^_]+)_", 1, AppName)
| summarize duration=toint((max(Timestamp)-min(Timestamp))/1m) by AppName_,AppId,WorkspaceId
| summarize sum(duration) by AppName_

SparkDerivedTaskMetrics
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where AppId == _applicationId
| summarize dcount(StageId)
//| summarize DistintStages=count_distinct(tostring(rsn))

SparkDerivedTaskMetrics
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where AppId == _applicationId
| where Status != "Success"
| summarize count()

SparkEventLogs 
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where EventDetailsJson contains "SparkListenerTaskEnd"
| where AppId =~ _applicationId
| summarize count() by execID=tolong(EventDetailsJson.["properties"].["Task Info"].["Executor ID"])
| order by execID asc

SparkEventLogs
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where AppId == _applicationId
| where EventDetailsJson contains "SparkListenerTaskEnd"
| extend props=parse_json(EventDetailsJson)
| extend rsn=props["properties"]['Task End Reason']['Reason']
| summarize Count=count() by RSN=tostring(rsn)

SparkEventLogs
| where AppId == _applicationId
| where EventType == "SparkListenerEnvironmentUpdate"
| extend sparkProperties = PropertiesJson.["Spark Properties"]
| mv-expand sparkProperties
| extend Property = tostring(bag_keys(sparkProperties)[0])
| extend Value = tostring(sparkProperties[Property])
| project Property, Value
| where Property in (
    "spark.trident.highconcurrency.enabled", 
    "spark.native.enabled", 
    "spark.synapse.vhd.id", 
    "spark.fabric.resourceProfile",
    "spark.databricks.delta.optimizeWrite.binSize",
    "spark.sql.parquet.vorder.default",
    "spark.databricks.delta.optimizeWrite.enabled"
    )
| extend Preperty = case(
    Property == "spark.native.enabled", "Native Execution Engine Enabled",
    Property == "spark.trident.highconcurrency.enabled", "Highconcurrency Enabled",
    Property == "spark.synapse.vhd.id", "Container ID",
    Property == "spark.fabric.resourceProfile", "Fabric Resource Profile",
    Property == "spark.databricks.delta.optimizeWrite.binSize", "Delta Optimize Write Bin Size",
    Property == "spark.sql.parquet.vorder.default", "VOrder Enabled",
    Property == "spark.databricks.delta.optimizeWrite.enabled", "Optimize Write Enabled",
    Property
)

SparkDerivedTaskMetrics 
| where AppId =~_applicationId
| project TaskId,EfficiencyRatio
| order by TaskId asc

TaskEndEvents_Filtered
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where AppId =~_applicationId
| extend EventDetails = parse_json(EventDetailsJson)
| project TaskId,executorID = EventDetails.["properties"].["Task Info"].["Executor ID"] , MemoryUsed = todouble(EventDetails.["properties"].["Task Metrics"].["Peak Executor Memory Used"])/1048576
| order by TaskId

SparkDerivedTaskMetrics 
| where AppId == _applicationId
| project TaskId,GcOverheadRatio
| order by TaskId asc

SparkEventLogs
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where AppId =~_applicationId
| where EventDetailsJson contains "SparkListenerTaskEnd"
| extend MetricsJson=parse_json(MetricsJson),EventDetailsJson=parse_json(EventDetailsJson)
| extend TaskId=toint(TaskId),TotalShuffleRead=tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Read Metrics"].["Remote Bytes Read"])+tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Read Metrics"].["Local Bytes Read"]),TotalShuffleWrite=tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Write Metrics"].["Shuffle Bytes Written"])  ,BytesRead= (tolong(MetricsJson["Input Metrics"].["Bytes Read"])) ,ShuffleOverheadRatio= todouble(todouble(tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Read Metrics"].["Remote Bytes Read"])+tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Read Metrics"].["Local Bytes Read"])+tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Write Metrics"].["Shuffle Bytes Written"]))) /todouble((tolong(MetricsJson["Input Metrics"].["Bytes Read"])))
| order by TaskId asc
| project TaskId,TotalShuffleRead,TotalShuffleWrite,BytesRead,ShuffleOverheadRatio

SparkEventLogs
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where AppId =~ _applicationId
| extend EventDetailsJson=parse_json(EventDetailsJson),MetricsJson=parse_json(MetricsJson)
| where EventDetailsJson contains "SparkListenerTaskEnd"
| project AppId,TaskId=toint(EventDetailsJson.["Task Info"].["Task ID"]),tolong(MetricsJson.["Memory Bytes Spilled"]) , tolong(MetricsJson.["Disk Bytes Spilled"])
| order by TaskId

SparkEventLogs
| where Timestamp between (_startTime .. _endTime)
| where AppId =~ _applicationId
| project AppName
| take 1

SparkEventLogs

| where isnotempty(EventDetailsJson.["properties"].["Executor Info"].["Total Cores"])

SparkEventLogs

| where EventDetailsJson contains "SparkListenerTaskEnd"
| extend MetricsJson=parse_json(MetricsJson),EventDetailsJson=parse_json(EventDetailsJson)
| extend TaskId=toint(TaskId),TotalShuffleRead=tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Read Metrics"].["Remote Bytes Read"])+tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Read Metrics"].["Local Bytes Read"]),TotalShuffleWrite=tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Write Metrics"].["Shuffle Bytes Written"])  ,BytesRead= (tolong(MetricsJson["Input Metrics"].["Bytes Read"])) ,ShuffleOverheadRatio= todouble(todouble(tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Read Metrics"].["Remote Bytes Read"])+tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Read Metrics"].["Local Bytes Read"])+tolong(MetricsJson["Shuffle Write Metrics"].["Shuffle Bytes Written"]))) /todouble((tolong(MetricsJson["Input Metrics"].["Bytes Read"])))
